'''Oro woods''' were once-famous trees from [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. They grew to be hundreds of feet tall and were covered in rainbow-colored glowing lichen. They grew on only a dozen small islands and were wiped out when the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station/Legends|first Death Star]] destroyed the planet, although a number of them were transplanted to [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Deer/Legends|Red deer]] and [[Cairoka/Legends|cairoka birds]] lived within the oro woods.

[[Orowood]] on Coruscant was named after them.

